Flare B0A Evidence Package
==========================

Purpose and result
------------------

This directory preserves the preregistered Flare B0A candidate universe, human-reviewed
assignments, deterministic adjudication outputs, and exact patch evidence needed for offline
replay. The initial round froze 62 candidates. The expanded round froze 526 candidates and
produced 7 independent configuration-only proposed fix groups, 10 proposed cases, and 4 proposed
defect classes. It produced no qualified_candidate or accepted cases. The fixed 8-group/4-class
investment gate therefore ended with status=insufficient_evidence, the sole failure reason
"fewer than eight independent proposed groups", and next_action=stop_flare_heavy_investment.

This is evidence of a completed negative investment gate, not a claim that Flare is a rich or
validated GameForge benchmark corpus. B0B qualification, corpus freeze, the production reader,
and checker evaluation were not entered.

