Evaluation disclosure
---------------------

The search had prior exploratory work that inspected Flare history before registration. The exact
two-round search was committed before harness discovery and exhausted its registered rules and reachable range,
but this is non-blind, purposive evidence search and not a blind or held-out sample. Issue and
pull-request discovery was disabled. The candidate-selection recall is unknown. The package does not
support population-wide claims about all Flare defects or all defects discoverable under other
search rules.

Mining commands
---------------

The commands below are the exact resolved GameForge mining invocations used for discovery and
offline adjudication. Both human approvals were added to their evidence payloads before the
corresponding final adjudication.

uv run python -m gameforge.bench.flare_mining discover --repo /tmp/gameforge-flare-game.git --search-spec scenarios/flare_corpus/search-spec.json --registration-commit 140aa5b99e9748022d735e67014c0bb8bd67cc77 --registration-path scenarios/flare_corpus/search-spec.json --round initial --out scenarios/flare_corpus/b0a/initial/candidate-ledger.discovered.json --blob-dir scenarios/flare_corpus/blobs

uv run python -m gameforge.bench.flare_mining adjudicate --ledger scenarios/flare_corpus/b0a/initial/candidate-ledger.discovered.json --evidence scenarios/flare_corpus/b0a/initial/adjudication-evidence.json --blob-dir scenarios/flare_corpus/blobs --out scenarios/flare_corpus/b0a/initial/candidate-ledger.json --decision-out scenarios/flare_corpus/b0a/initial/b0a-decision.json

