Mixed-license patch evidence
----------------------------

blobs/ contains 519 content-addressed, complete Git binary patches retained for all proposed,
rejected, and ambiguous candidate assignments. Before deduplication, the 526 candidate references
account for 332,834,369 patch bytes. Content addressing stores 306,007,216 unique bytes, saving
26,827,153 bytes while preserving every reference. The patches include configuration and data text,
C++ and Python source hunks, images, audio, and font binary deltas. They are not merely a set of
configuration excerpts. Patches are retained as audit evidence, not as a checkout or runnable
redistribution of the whole game. This limited purpose does not replace the license terms for the
upstream material actually present in those patches.

